OpenPI π0.5 for DexJoCo

This repository is derived from OpenPI, originally released under the
Apache License, Version 2.0.

DexJoCo-specific modifications include:

- DexJoCo LeRobot data configs and normalization assets.
- Single-arm and bimanual DexJoCo policy input/output adapters.
- π0.5 action-dimension conversion utilities for 44-dimensional bimanual actions.
- DexJoCo training, normalization, and tmux launch scripts.
- Documentation and installation workflow for DexJoCo π0.5 training and serving.

Files and examples unrelated to DexJoCo training may be omitted from this
distribution.

